# Agentic tools

Read [agentic-tools/README.md](agentic-tools/README.md) and [AGENTS.md](AGENTS.md) before changing bindings or manifests.

## Required after manifest / codegen hook edits

```bash
dotnet run --project codegen/Novolis.Raylib.CodeGen -- generate
pwsh ./scripts/agent-verify.ps1
```

Machine-readable catalog: [agentic-tools/registry.json](agentic-tools/registry.json).

## Never

- Hand-edit `*.g.cs` in `Novolis.Raylib.Bindings/Interop/` or `Novolis.Raylib.Runtime/`
- Put publishable packages under `codegen/`
- Skip committing regenerated `*.g.cs` when manifests change
